description: This file serves as the entry point for a React application. It imports React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React DOM root and renders the App component inside a StrictMode wrapper.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root DOM node for rendering a React app in the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree starting from <App /> inside the root DOM node.
